HEADWORD: Ant-bear
<hw>Ant"-bear`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>An edentate animal of tropical America (the <xex>Tamanoir</xex>),
living on ants. It belongs to the genus
<gen>Myrmecophaga</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ant bird</ent>⟦br⟧
